-top: 24px; font-size: 16px;"&gt; Ben &amp;amp; Jerry&amp;#39;s 不仅以冰淇淋而闻名，还因其对社会事业的支持而闻名。去年销售额超过 10 亿美元，对于其所有者 Magnum 来说是一笔资产。那么，为什么其中一位创始人辞职，而另一位创始人发起了一场运动，让 Ben &amp;amp; Jerry&amp;#39;s 独立呢？&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style="margin-top: 24px; font-size: 16px;"&gt;彭博社的阿克沙特·拉蒂 (Akshat Rathi) 与联合创始人本·科恩 (Ben Cohen) 坐下来询问“免费本和杰瑞”运动、为什么企业应该追求社会事业以及冰淇淋在变暖的星球上的未来。&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style="margin-top: 24px; font-size: 16px;"&gt;&lt;em style="font-size: 16px;"&gt;立即收听，并在&lt;/em&gt;&lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/s/c/QXvAVQDbd_gfUcaFH5HXum0U5EzT0CXD5xfQLK0yUW61YeUd5Hd8Wz1Dh5C1y-bH3Z3EgWBr0gbW1S6_Dhxpdy_pIMQBV7Pdei0dxNZFHeRWVJNWD2I648mqegWJr19txqC2LKcf7olNpvU1-67nPgvJhHcpFijkIt2Mtv_y7FhXUyYjcVUmCxIiIPRyfbhXWsz9ibZm0cW52RlRd6TFnzMsytOIp80oMi3wWMO58Xguj9IYnKjrBdgK5Bitl_s4Fu7X1LRhj03ESJznJi2C3-41ux0SdRMmhS3FNaOC6GLqQbDKGJZR_UDaKK3_9T8Sox2mLA/wO9iEZBqr8uSEXIUwayF5nIfaAzA1UBn/21?cmpid=BBD061226_GREENDAILY&amp;amp;utm_campaign=greendaily&amp;amp;utm_medium=email&amp;amp;utm_source=newsletter&amp;amp;utm_term=260612&amp;amp;utm_content=5467" rel="noopener noreferrer" style="font-size: inherit; color: #00e;" target="_blank" title="零：气候竞赛"&gt;&lt;em style="font-size: 16px;"&gt;Apple&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/a&gt; &lt;em style="font-size: 16px;"&gt;、&lt;/em&gt; &lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/s/c/LSVW3hjB23VxsROtR09BeGaaqF6323Mivbp393IrMgEmUkAdRZnbhQhiBO2sptqPW3g980Nr5j6M2BucZDgBxeG6Ce2pCc815gf0eUK1i3MU1nO_ccpQuLdz-XVRbH7UXKJ30innXmCU3TKLUHffCmHm13OlBg7rjJbpz_IC13OdWV7QtDS1UxEwtcXRpMwmbVT2Xa3rjBxsjpd8BJslef3tDNXpPhru1UTk4AID97TBptpsXQfs9-PWiHAlVvMtX0hVh9-nXN-rgpxsypejVq6XhLnpiUQm4H9afNOJVYlvLMyxnJVeY-lfx6__DbMx2kMOwPDFuvOuLHoUDP6ZmdvvWVCM/NBWXKYvAEvjhdMmuRHlAz6k-bxA5X0ZK/21?cmpid=BBD061226_GREENDAILY&amp;amp;utm_campaign=greendaily&amp;amp;utm_medium=email&amp;amp;utm_source=newsletter&amp;amp;utm_term=260612&amp;amp;utm_content=5467" rel="noopener noreferrer" style="font-size: inherit; color: #00e;" target="_blank" title="零：气候竞赛"&gt;&lt;em style="font-size: 16px;"&gt;Spotify&